Revision history for IO-Prompt-I18N

0.78    2014-12-11 (PERLANCAR)

	- [ux] Tweak condition for showing choice of words.

	- [Bugfix] Forgot to add confirm()'s default texts.


0.77    2014-12-11 (PERLANCAR)

        - Rename module/dist from SHARYANTO-Text-Prompt to IO-Prompt-I18N.

        - confirm(): Add options 'lang', 'yes_words', 'no_words'. Support
          several languages: en, fr, id.

        - prompt(): Add option 'show_default'.


0.76    2014-10-11 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release, split from SHARYANTO-Utils to reduce dependencies.

        - Add function: confirm().
